@{
    ViewBag.Title = "Privacy Policy";
}
<div class="privacy-container">
    <div class="background-elements">
        <div class="grid-overlay"></div>
        <div class="glow-orb primary"></div>
        <div class="glow-orb accent"></div>
        <div class="tech-rings">
            <div class="ring outer"></div>
            <div class="ring middle"></div>
            <div class="ring inner"></div>
            <div class="pulse-dot"></div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="privacy-content">
        <div class="section-heading">
            <span class="heading-badge">Your Data, Our Priority</span>
            <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
            <div class="heading-underline"></div>
        </div>

        <div class="privacy-text">
            <p class="intro-text">
                At DevuSec, based in Amman, Jordan, we are committed to protecting your privacy and ensuring the security of your personal information. This Privacy Policy outlines how we collect, use, store, and protect your data when you interact with our services, website, or contact us. Last updated: April 12, 2025.
            </p>

            <div class="policy-section">
                <h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>
                <p>
                    We collect information to provide better services and ensure a seamless user experience. This includes:
                </p>
                <ul class="privacy-list">
                    <li><strong>Personal Information</strong>: Name, email address, phone number, and other details you provide when contacting us or using our services.</li>
                    <li><strong>Usage Data</strong>: Information about how you interact with our website, such as IP address, browser type, pages visited, and time spent.</li>
                    <li><strong>Cookies</strong>: We use cookies and similar technologies to enhance your browsing experience and analyze site performance. You can manage cookie preferences via your browser settings.</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="policy-section">
                <h2>2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
                <p>
                    Your data helps us improve our services and communicate effectively. We use it to:
                </p>
                <ul class="privacy-list">
                    <li>Respond to your inquiries and provide customer support.</li>
                    <li>Analyze website usage to enhance functionality and user experience.</li>
                    <li>Send promotional materials or updates, with your consent, about our services.</li>
                    <li>Comply with legal obligations under Jordanian law.</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="policy-section">
                <h2>3. Data Storage and Security</h2>
                <p>
                    We store your data securely using industry-standard encryption and access controls. Data is retained only for as long as necessary to fulfill the purposes outlined in this policy or as required by law. Our servers are hosted in secure facilities compliant with international standards.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="policy-section">
                <h2>4. Sharing Your Information</h2>
                <p>
                    We do not sell or rent your personal information. We may share data with:
                </p>
                <ul class="privacy-list">
                    <li>Trusted third-party service providers (e.g., hosting or analytics providers) who adhere to strict privacy standards.</li>
                    <li>Legal authorities, if required by Jordanian law or to protect our rights.</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="policy-section">
                <h2>5. Your Rights</h2>
                <p>
                    As a user, you have the right to:
                </p>
                <ul class="privacy-list">
                    <li>Access, correct, or delete your personal information.</li>
                    <li>Opt out of marketing communications at any time.</li>
                    <li>Request information about how your data is processed.</li>
                    <li>Lodge a complaint with a supervisory authority if you believe your privacy rights have been violated.</li>
                </ul>
                <p>
                    To exercise these rights, contact us at <a href="mailto:privacy@techsec.com">privacy@techsec.com</a>.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="policy-section">
                <h2>6. International Data Transfers</h2>
                <p>
                    As a Jordan-based company, we primarily process data within Jordan. If data is transferred internationally (e.g., to cloud providers), we ensure compliance with applicable data protection laws and use safeguards like standard contractual clauses.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="policy-section">
                <h2>7. Cookies and Tracking</h2>
                <p>
                    Our website uses cookies to improve functionality and analyze traffic. You can disable cookies in your browser, but this may limit some features. We respect "Do Not Track" signals where applicable.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="policy-section">
                <h2>8. Changes to This Policy</h2>
                <p>
                    We may update this Privacy Policy to reflect changes in our practices or legal requirements. Updates will be posted on this page with a revised "Last updated" date. We encourage you to review this policy periodically.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="policy-section">
                <h2>9. Contact Us</h2>
                <p>
                    If you have questions about this Privacy Policy or our data practices, please reach out to us:
                </p>
                <ul class="privacy-list contact-info">
                    <li><strong>Email</strong>: <a href="mailto:privacy@techsec.com">privacy@techsec.com</a></li>
                    <li><strong>Phone</strong>: +962 (79) 509-5985</li>
                    <li><strong>Address</strong>: SecuDev, Amman, Jordan</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<style>
   

    /* Reset and Base Styles */
    * {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    html, body {
        height: 100%;
        width: 100%;
        overflow-x: hidden;
        scroll-behavior: smooth;
    }

    body {
        background-color: var(--dark-bg);
        color: var(--text-primary);
        font-family: 'Inter', 'SF Pro Display', system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif;
        line-height: 1.6;
        font-weight: 400;
        -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
        -moz-osx-font-smoothing: grayscale;
    }

    /* Container and Layout */
    .privacy-container {
        position: relative;
        width: 100%;
        min-height: 100vh;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        padding: 40px 20px;
        z-index: 1;
        overflow: hidden;
    }

    /* Background Elements */
    .background-elements {
        position: fixed;
        top: 0;
        left: 0;
        width: 100%;
        height: 100%;
        z-index: -1;
        overflow: hidden;
    }

    .grid-overlay {
        position: absolute;
        width: 400%;
        height: 400%;
        top: -150%;
        left: -150%;
        background-image: linear-gradient(rgba(0, 229, 255, 0.05) 1px, transparent 1px), linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(0, 229, 255, 0.05) 1px, transparent 1px);
        background-size: 40px 40px;
        transform: perspective(1000px) rotateX(60deg) scale(1.5);
        animation: gridFloat 60s linear infinite;
        opacity: 0.4;
    }

    @@keyframes gridFloat {
        0% {
            transform: perspective(1000px) rotateX(60deg) scale(1.5) translateY(0);
        }

        100% {
            transform: perspective(1000px) rotateX(60deg) scale(1.5) translateY(40px);
        }
    }

    .glow-orb {
        position: absolute;
        border-radius: 50%;
        filter: blur(120px);
        opacity: 0.5;
        animation: orbPulse 12s ease-in-out infinite alternate;
    }

        .glow-orb.primary {
            width: 140vh;
            height: 140vh;
            background: radial-gradient(circle, var(--primary-glow) 0%, rgba(0, 229, 255, 0) 70%);
            bottom: -70vh;
            right: -20vh;
        }

        .glow-orb.accent {
            width: 100vh;
            height: 100vh;
            background: radial-gradient(circle, var(--accent-glow) 0%, rgba(255, 0, 229, 0) 70%);
            top: -50vh;
            left: -30vh;
            animation-delay: -6s;
        }

    @@keyframes orbPulse {
        0% {
            opacity: 0.3;
            transform: scale(0.9);
        }

        100% {
            opacity: 0.6;
            transform: scale(1.1);
        }
    }

    .tech-rings {
        position: absolute;
        top: 50%;
        left: 50%;
        transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
        z-index: 0;
    }

    .ring {
        position: absolute;
        top: 50%;
        left: 50%;
        border-radius: 50%;
        border: 1px solid rgba(0, 229, 255, 0.2);
        transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
    }

        .ring.outer {
            width: 500px;
            height: 500px;
            animation: spin 40s linear infinite;
        }

        .ring.middle {
            width: 350px;
            height: 350px;
            animation: spin 30s linear infinite reverse;
        }

        .ring.inner {
            width: 200px;
            height: 200px;
            animation: spin 20s linear infinite;
        }

    @@keyframes spin {
        from {
            transform: translate(-50%, -50%) rotate(0deg);
        }

        to {
            transform: translate(-50%, -50%) rotate(360deg);
        }
    }

    .pulse-dot {
        position: absolute;
        top: 50%;
        left: 50%;
        width: 60px;
        height: 60px;
        background: rgba(0, 229, 255, 0.3);
        border-radius: 50%;
        transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
        animation: pulse 3s ease-in-out infinite;
    }

        .pulse-dot::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 50%;
            left: 50%;
            width: 24px;
            height: 24px;
            background: var(--primary-color);
            border-radius: 50%;
            transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px var(--primary-color);
        }

    @@keyframes pulse {
        0% {
            transform: translate(-50%, -50%) scale(0.8);
            opacity: 0.8;
        }

        50% {
            transform: translate(-50%, -50%) scale(1.4);
            opacity: 1;
        }

        100% {
            transform: translate(-50%, -50%) scale(0.8);
            opacity: 0.8;
        }
    }

    /* Content Styling */
    .privacy-content {
        width: 100%;
        max-width: 1200px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        background: var(--card-bg);
        border: 1px solid var(--border-light);
        border-radius: 24px;
        padding: 60px;
        backdrop-filter: var(--glass-blur);
        -webkit-backdrop-filter: var(--glass-blur);
        box-shadow: var(--box-shadow);
        transition: var(--transition-smooth);
        animation: fadeIn 1s ease-out;
        opacity: 0;
        animation-fill-mode: forwards;
    }

    @@keyframes fadeIn {
        from {
            opacity: 0;
            transform: translateY(30px);
        }

        to {
            opacity: 1;
            transform: translateY(0);
        }
    }

    .privacy-content:hover {
        box-shadow: 0 30px 60px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
        transform: translateY(-5px);
    }

    /* Section Headings */
    .section-heading {
        margin-bottom: 40px;
        text-align: center;
    }

    .heading-badge {
        display: inline-block;
        background: linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(0, 229, 255, 0.2), rgba(255, 0, 229, 0.2));
        color: var(--text-bright);
        font-size: 0.9rem;
        font-weight: 600;
        padding: 8px 16px;
        border-radius: 100px;
        margin-bottom: 16px;
        backdrop-filter: var(--glass-blur);
        border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
    }

    h1 {
        font-size: 3.5rem;
        font-weight: 800;
        margin: 0;
        background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--primary-color), var(--accent-color));
        -webkit-background-clip: text;
        background-clip: text;
        -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
        letter-spacing: -1px;
        line-height: 1.1;
    }

    .heading-underline {
        width: 100px;
        height: 4px;
        background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--primary-color), var(--accent-color));
        margin: 20px auto 0;
        border-radius: 2px;
    }

    .intro-text {
        color: var(--text-secondary);
        max-width: 800px;
        margin: 0 auto 50px;
        font-size: 1.1rem;
        text-align: center;
        line-height: 1.8;
    }

    /* Policy Sections */
    .policy-section {
        margin-bottom: 40px;
        animation: sectionFadeIn 0.5s ease-out;
        animation-fill-mode: both;
        opacity: 0;
    }

        .policy-section:nth-child(2) {
            animation-delay: 0.1s;
        }

        .policy-section:nth-child(3) {
            animation-delay: 0.2s;
        }

        .policy-section:nth-child(4) {
            animation-delay: 0.3s;
        }

        .policy-section:nth-child(5) {
            animation-delay: 0.4s;
        }

        .policy-section:nth-child(6) {
            animation-delay: 0.5s;
        }

        .policy-section:nth-child(7) {
            animation-delay: 0.6s;
        }

        .policy-section:nth-child(8) {
            animation-delay: 0.7s;
        }

        .policy-section:nth-child(9) {
            animation-delay: 0.8s;
        }

    @@keyframes sectionFadeIn {
        from {
            opacity: 0;
            transform: translateY(20px);
        }

        to {
            opacity: 1;
            transform: translateY(0);
        }
    }

    h2 {
        font-size: 1.8rem;
        font-weight: 600;
        color: var(--text-bright);
        margin-bottom: 16px;
        display: inline-block;
        position: relative;
    }

        h2::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            left: 0;
            bottom: -6px;
            width: 40px;
            height: 3px;
            background: var(--primary-color);
            border-radius: 2px;
        }

    /* Lists and Text */
    .privacy-list {
        list-style: none;
        padding: 0;
        margin: 16px 0 24px;
    }

        .privacy-list li {
            position: relative;
            padding-left: 28px;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            color: var(--text-secondary);
        }

            .privacy-list li::before {
                content: '';
                position: absolute;
                left: 0;
                top: 10px;
                width: 10px;
                height: 10px;
                background: var(--primary-color);
                border-radius: 50%;
                opacity: 0.7;
            }

    .privacy-text p {
        margin-bottom: 16px;
        color: var(--text-secondary);
    }

    a {
        color: var(--primary-color);
        text-decoration: none;
        transition: var(--transition-smooth);
        border-bottom: 1px dashed rgba(0, 229, 255, 0.3);
        padding-bottom: 2px;
    }

        a:hover {
            color: var(--primary-hover);
            border-bottom-color: var(--primary-hover);
        }

    .contact-info li {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
    }

        .contact-info li strong {
            min-width: 80px;
            display: inline-block;
            color: var(--text-bright);
        }

    /* Responsive Adjustments */
    @@media (max-width: 1200px) {
        .privacy-content {
            padding: 50px;
            max-width: 90%;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 3rem;
        }
    }

    @@media (max-width: 768px) {
        .privacy-container {
            padding: 20px 15px;
        }

        .privacy-content {
            padding: 40px 30px;
            max-width: 100%;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
        }

        h2 {
            font-size: 1.6rem;
        }

        .intro-text {
            font-size: 1rem;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }

        .ring.outer {
            width: 350px;
            height: 350px;
        }

        .ring.middle {
            width: 250px;
            height: 250px;
        }

        .ring.inner {
            width: 150px;
            height: 150px;
        }
    }

    @@media (max-width: 480px) {
        .privacy-content {
            padding: 30px 20px;
            border-radius: 16px;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 2rem;
        }

        h2 {
            font-size: 1.4rem;
        }

        .heading-badge {
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            padding: 6px 12px;
        }

        .privacy-list li {
            padding-left: 22px;
        }

            .privacy-list li::before {
                width: 8px;
                height: 8px;
            }

        .ring.outer {
            width: 250px;
            height: 250px;
        }

        .ring.middle {
            width: 180px;
            height: 180px;
        }

        .ring.inner {
            width: 100px;
            height: 100px;
        }

        .pulse-dot {
            width: 40px;
            height: 40px;
        }

            .pulse-dot::after {
                width: 16px;
                height: 16px;
            }
    }
</style>